title: Can't Access my Match History ever on the website.
body: Can anybody help me in this situation? On this website, na.leagueoflegends.com, I have not been able to view or access my match history for a few weeks. I thought the issue would just go away, but it has not yet. Is there anyway or anything I can do to get to see it? When I click on the match history tab under my profile, it just sits there on the match history page, but doesn't ever load in. The link I provided shows you what I see when I click Match History tab on the website.

replies.body:
Hmmm.. There could be a few things that may be causing this. I'd first recommend [**clearing your browser's cache**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies), then trying to view your match history using [**this link**](http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-history/NA1/219093390).

Let me know if this worked for you.
I cleared my browser's cache "since the beginning of time", but still don't have access to view my match history.

Since those workarounds didn't work for you, I recommend you report this in our [**Bug Tracker**](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report). We're aware of this issue with the match history webpage and are looking into it, but I don't have a timeline on when a fix will roll out for this.

Hit me up if you have any other questions.
